The described files are part of a monitoring-etc-setup on a Debian/Ubuntu linuxhost.

 - ./apt.conf.d contains configuration for the apt-hook
 - ./cron.d contains a trigger for the fsvs cron-job
 - ./etc contains fsvs config files
 - ./etc/ssl, fsvs config file for access of secured repositories
 - ./ignore, a sample ignore ruleset
